data.description: Moments from Emery High School & local amenities, friendly neighborhood roads lead you to this two-story abode & an attached studio unit in Emeryville. A covered entry reveals an open living space basked in natural light. Step across durable flooring to reach the well-equipped kitchen with shaker cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, & stone countertops accompanying contemporary tile backsplash. Leave the glass slider ajar & allow a fresh breeze to cool the living area, or step out to a deck that overlooks the backyard oasis. On the main level, a primary suite features an immaculate ensuite with a luxurious glass-encased shower. On the lower level, three additional bedrooms are coupled with two full-hall baths. As if the main home wasn't abundant enough, a 427 Sqft attached studio unit offers a place for long-term guests or makes an incredible rental opportunity. When you're ready to venture out of your peaceful abode, you're surrounded by endless eateries, shopping centers, & entertainment.
